title: St Paul's CREATE Fertility Open Day - December 5th 2015
desc: We are pleased to announce a new Open Day at our St Paul's clinic where any new patient interested in learning more about infertility treatments can: We also offer you the opportunity to have a personal 10-minute one-on-one chat with  Professors or Lead Consultants , which is extremely useful in helping you make an informed decision on fertility treatment. This event starts from 11.00am, please arrive promptly Directions and parking information Our St Paul's Clinic is easily accessible by public transport. It is next to St Paul's tube station, other close by stations include Bank, Mansion House, Barbican, City Thameslink and Blackfriars. There are several close by car parks, the nearest being on Queen Victoria Street. There is also on-street parking nearby. ? Please note, this event is not for existing patients.
